      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-Arm SIG 是什么？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "openEuler sig-Arm SIG（Special Interest Group，特别兴趣小组）负责 SIG Arm focus on Kunpeng, Phytium and other Arm architecture hardware software ecosystem adoption.。该 SIG 共有 9 名核心成员，维护 1 个代码仓库，属于 基础设施与工具 领域。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "如何参与 openEuler sig-Arm SIG？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
          "text": "参与 openEuler sig-Arm SIG 的方式：1）向相关仓库（如 openeuler/arm）提交 Pull Request；2）订阅邮件列表 dev@openeuler.org；3）参加 SIG 定期工作会议，会议信息见 openEuler 官网活动日历。"
        }
      },
      {
        "@type": "Question",
        "name": "openEuler sig-Arm SIG 包含哪些代码仓库？",
        "acceptedAnswer": {
          "@type": "Answer",
